description:
Meet the classic puzzle in a modern version! Show your strategic thinking and logic skills to connect all the dots and complete all levels!

The rules of the game are simple - you need to connect all the dots with lines so that the lines do not intersect. But the further you go, the harder the puzzles become. So it's time to stretch your brain!

The game has appearance settings, so you can easily customize the game for yourself.

Key features:
• Excellent workout for the mind and logic;
• Many levels with different difficulty;
• Customization of the playing field and elements;
• Management with the Joy-Con™️ controllers;
• Relaxing musical accompaniment;
